description: Jake is a 19 year old college wrestler from Minnesota.He's an incredibly athletic person and has tons of energy-- not to mention sexual drive. He seemed very shy to us at first, but once his pants came off, he was wild. Our staff had a fun time working with Jake, and even partied with him after the shoot. He's quite the drinker, although has an enormous tolerance and manages to drink beer after beer without it affecting him at all. Must be the metabolism... this guy is in awesome shape.Jake is a very sensual person, and puts on a nice show for the camera. Watch him in three scenes. Living room, followed by bathroom/shower. Then he finishes off in the bedroom. We think you'll like what you see. We sure did.
title: Jake
